the county town of County Monaghan, Ireland. Its population at the 2011 census
was 7,452 including suburbs and environs. The town is on the N2 road from Dublin
to Derry and Letterkenny.<ref>http://www.hse.ie/eng/staff/Resources/FactFile/He-
